description:
The Premarital Bootcamp is a great way to learn more about each other and firm-up the strong foundation your relationship has been built on as "Me" becomes "We".

Learn about the assets that each of you bring to the table that make your relationship unique, and how to use these tools on more challenging areas.

Together, you will:

  • Discover you and your partner's relationship wishes
  • Understand Each Others Communication
  • Practice Conflict Resolution on Real Issues
  • Understand the meaning of money in your relationship
  • Examine family spiritual beliefs
  • Discuss leisure activities
  • Understand what affection and intimacy mean to each of you
title: Walk down the Aisle Together Closer & Happier Than Ever!
